The paper focuses on object detection using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of multiple experts and selective/exhaustive search techniques also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects. Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the proposed approach on different datasets, which relates to information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
